1
00:00:07,220 --> 00:00:11,820
♪She looks at the bright moon
hanging high above the clouds♪

2
00:00:11,860 --> 00:00:14,140
♪And I fall into the mountains♪

3
00:00:14,220 --> 00:00:16,100
♪Protect this broken world♪

4
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:20,620
♪A faint wish♪

5
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:23,900
♪Life is just a dream,
isn't the world so?♪

6
00:00:23,980 --> 00:00:27,620
♪Looking back,
I count the joys of my remaining years♪

7
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:31,020
♪It's difficult to see you in my dreams♪

8
00:00:31,060 --> 00:00:33,940
♪Ignoring the coldness of the world,
I still linger♪

9
00:00:33,980 --> 00:00:37,300
♪Love and hate are intertwined,
not just in the past♪

10
00:00:37,340 --> 00:00:40,900
♪The past is painful,
and time goes by in a flash♪

11
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:44,500
♪Stars fall on the mountain top again♪

12
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:48,140
♪My heart is as pure as the moon
and connected to you♪

13
00:00:54,140 --> 00:00:56,980
[No One But You]

14
00:00:56,980 --> 00:01:01,980
[Episode 16]
[Let's live together in this abyss.]

15
00:01:31,540 --> 00:01:33,700
What new tricks do you have now?

16
00:01:43,580 --> 00:01:44,460
Jiang Mohan,

17
00:01:45,340 --> 00:01:46,340
I'm tired.

18
00:01:47,020 --> 00:01:48,500
Can we let each other go?

19
00:01:54,740 --> 00:01:55,740
Let each other go?

20
00:01:58,940 --> 00:02:00,660
Do you think I'll still believe you?

21
00:02:01,580 --> 00:02:03,500
If you are going
to imprison me like this,

22
00:02:03,820 --> 00:02:04,980
you might as well kill me.

23
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:19,060
Dream on.

24
00:02:19,700 --> 00:02:21,780
You will never get away

25
00:02:22,420 --> 00:02:23,860
unless I'm dead.

26
00:02:26,540 --> 00:02:28,180
Now that you hate to kill me,

27
00:02:28,900 --> 00:02:29,860
let's live together

28
00:02:29,860 --> 00:02:32,060
in this abyss.

29
00:02:33,140 --> 00:02:34,380
But now,

30
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:36,660
I want to go to Joys of Life to unwind.

31
00:02:41,300 --> 00:02:42,100
Okay.

32
00:02:43,900 --> 00:02:45,060
I'll go with you.

33
00:02:56,180 --> 00:02:57,980
Miss Yu, it's been a while
since you came.

34
00:02:58,460 --> 00:03:00,780
I need to get the message to Fan.

35
00:03:01,380 --> 00:03:03,580
Yeah, it's been a while.

36
00:03:04,140 --> 00:03:05,220
How about

37
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:07,180
me performing a song for you today?

38
00:03:07,180 --> 00:03:08,100
That sounds great.

39
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:41,200
♪The sky of the South
is thousands of miles away♪

40
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:45,620
♪Colorful clouds disperse easily,
while faint mist lingers over the waves♪

41
00:03:46,470 --> 00:03:50,910
♪The strong wind and swift sail
make it difficult to turn back♪

42
00:03:52,020 --> 00:03:56,120
♪My beloved is trimming the candle,
holding on to a cold night♪

43
00:03:57,370 --> 00:04:00,920
♪Gazing toward the horizon,
I sigh at the long road ahead♪

44
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:04,620
[Chu Yunfan has been exposed]*
[Using homophones in lyrics to alert]

45
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:08,380
Bravo!

46
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:13,940
Qinghuan,

47
00:04:14,620 --> 00:04:15,940
[Joys of Life]
that was a nice song.

48
00:04:16,980 --> 00:04:18,500
You are smart,

49
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:20,380
but don't take me as a fool.

50
00:04:22,180 --> 00:04:23,580
You want to kill him,

51
00:04:23,780 --> 00:04:25,340
but I am going to save him.

52
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:28,300
Isn't this what you want from a prey?

53
00:04:30,660 --> 00:04:32,500
Still thinking about Chu Yunfan, huh?

54
00:04:33,180 --> 00:04:33,980
Okay,

55
00:04:34,780 --> 00:04:36,100
I will have you watch

56
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:37,980
how he is going to die.

57
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:44,820
Watch everyone here carefully.

58
00:04:51,020 --> 00:04:53,070
[Criminal Case Autopsy Report]

59
00:04:53,660 --> 00:04:55,100
Chu Yunfan here

60
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:57,060
is fake.

61
00:04:57,860 --> 00:04:59,900
The real Young Leader
was shot through the left chest

62
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:01,780
when he was in Nanyan.

63
00:05:01,780 --> 00:05:02,980
He is dead.

64
00:05:07,380 --> 00:05:08,980
You tried so hard

65
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:10,180
and that's what you came up with?

66
00:05:10,660 --> 00:05:13,140
No wonder you haven't made it
to the leader all these years.

67
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:15,540
Whether this is true or not,

68
00:05:15,540 --> 00:05:16,580
a check will tell.

69
00:05:17,260 --> 00:05:18,660
Take off your clothes now.

70
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:19,580
What's with the talking?

71
00:05:47,820 --> 00:05:49,260
No killing today.

72
00:05:51,980 --> 00:05:52,700
Just here for the show.

73
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:55,500
Continue.

74
00:06:07,660 --> 00:06:08,460
What,

75
00:06:09,420 --> 00:06:10,060
are you afraid?

76
00:06:15,140 --> 00:06:16,500
If you don't have a bullet hole in you,

77
00:06:18,340 --> 00:06:20,300
I don't mind giving you one.

78
00:06:46,220 --> 00:06:46,780
It's there.

79
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:47,700
Yeah, there is one.

80
00:06:58,420 --> 00:06:59,620
I've got more evidence.

81
00:07:00,500 --> 00:07:01,300
Bring him in!

82
00:07:03,100 --> 00:07:05,260
The real Young Leader's classmate
in Nanyang

83
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:06,660
will check you out.

84
00:07:09,820 --> 00:07:11,700
Yunfan? You...

85
00:07:12,260 --> 00:07:14,220
I thought you were shot dead.

86
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:15,780
How come...?

87
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:18,460
Get him out!

88
00:07:23,700 --> 00:07:24,780
How could this be possible?

89
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:29,300
I was shot

90
00:07:29,780 --> 00:07:30,700
but luckily, I survived.

91
00:07:31,420 --> 00:07:33,380
I knew the killer would not let me go,

92
00:07:34,380 --> 00:07:35,900
so I faked my death and came back home

93
00:07:36,780 --> 00:07:37,900
to look for the culprit.

94
00:07:39,580 --> 00:07:41,220
The killer was your man, wasn't it?

95
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:42,660
Second Uncle?

96
00:07:55,860 --> 00:07:58,100
I'm indeed not the real Chu Yunfan.

97
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:21,170
[Criminal Case Autopsy Report]

98
00:08:25,300 --> 00:08:26,140
Hold it.

99
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:44,140
Are you okay?

100
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,100
[Chu Yunfan has been exposed.]

101
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:57,700
[A Qing Gang elder got evidence
including his autopsy report.]

102
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:02,380
Unfortunately,
you can never tell the truth.

103
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:13,940
Thanks to Qinghuan's message,

104
00:09:14,140 --> 00:09:14,980
I got fully prepared.

105
00:09:17,580 --> 00:09:18,860
Sorry, sir.

106
00:09:19,700 --> 00:09:20,780
You've come all the way

107
00:09:21,180 --> 00:09:22,260
for a show that isn't on.

108
00:09:23,220 --> 00:09:24,300
Sorry for the disappointment.

109
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:32,660
Looks like you'd had a backup plan.

110
00:09:33,460 --> 00:09:34,300
Qinghuan,

111
00:09:35,260 --> 00:09:37,580
we surely have a connection.

112
00:09:38,340 --> 00:09:39,420
What do you mean?

113
00:09:39,420 --> 00:09:40,100
Sir.

114
00:09:45,740 --> 00:09:47,500
We've successfully seized the wharf.

115
00:09:47,900 --> 00:09:49,140
What?

116
00:09:52,340 --> 00:09:53,500
I see.

117
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:55,620
You turned us against each other

118
00:09:55,940 --> 00:09:57,500
so you could take the wharf.

119
00:10:22,540 --> 00:10:23,940
I'll give you a pass today.

120
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:29,020
I will not give you a second chance

121
00:10:29,300 --> 00:10:31,300
to prove yourself.

122
00:10:40,260 --> 00:10:41,300
The show is over.

123
00:10:42,020 --> 00:10:42,820
Let's go.

124
00:10:56,500 --> 00:10:57,740
Get someone to drag him out.

125
00:10:57,740 --> 00:10:58,300
Yes, sir.

126
00:11:02,620 --> 00:11:05,140
Miss, here's the qipao you ordered.

127
00:11:05,140 --> 00:11:07,100
They said you could get it altered
if it doesn't fit.

128
00:11:08,260 --> 00:11:09,140
You may leave.

129
00:11:20,140 --> 00:11:22,380
The Marshal and the Japanese Chamber
of Commerce are about to cooperate

130
00:11:22,540 --> 00:11:24,340
and transport munitions
into the country.

131
00:11:24,580 --> 00:11:25,780
Please try to stop it.

132
00:11:38,820 --> 00:11:39,620
The Marshall called

133
00:11:39,780 --> 00:11:41,140
hoping you could consider
the bigger picture

134
00:11:41,540 --> 00:11:43,260
and agree to the marriage
with Miss Chihoko.

135
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:45,420
I see.

136
00:11:52,540 --> 00:11:53,580
Have you heard it?

137
00:11:55,060 --> 00:11:57,180
Should I congratulate you?

138
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:02,380
I don't allow you to.

139
00:12:03,820 --> 00:12:05,820
You know what I truly want.

140
00:12:06,780 --> 00:12:08,420
And you are not getting it.

141
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:10,900
The ending of us has been written.

142
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:13,140
Either one is killing the other

143
00:12:13,740 --> 00:12:15,620
or we'll kill each other.

144
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:19,220
Very well.

145
00:12:23,260 --> 00:12:24,620
But before that,

146
00:12:26,060 --> 00:12:28,020
I will have you share my pain

147
00:12:28,700 --> 00:12:32,260
and witness my joy.

148
00:12:45,020 --> 00:12:46,700
Mohan, you've finally come.

149
00:12:47,140 --> 00:12:48,900
Let me introduce you to my father.

150
00:12:50,100 --> 00:12:52,260
What a charming man.

151
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:54,540
No wonder my daughter likes you so much.

152
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:58,940
I'll leave you alone
for a nice family chat.

153
00:13:01,660 --> 00:13:03,940
Today is about you and Miss Chihoko.

154
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:04,940
Let's go.

155
00:13:05,300 --> 00:13:06,300
Let's go, Mohan.

156
00:13:14,300 --> 00:13:15,340
You are not Guzhou.

157
00:13:16,340 --> 00:13:17,420
The real Guzhou

158
00:13:17,700 --> 00:13:19,020
would not abandon his mission

159
00:13:19,020 --> 00:13:20,300
and take the risk of saving me.

160
00:13:20,740 --> 00:13:21,780
Who exactly are you?

161
00:13:32,860 --> 00:13:33,780
Qinghuan,

162
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:35,620
I don't want to hide it from you.

163
00:13:36,380 --> 00:13:38,180
I'm an undercover agent
for the Beizhou government.

164
00:13:38,380 --> 00:13:40,060
I've been ordered
to impersonate the Young Leader

165
00:13:40,580 --> 00:13:42,140
and investigate the munition smuggling.

166
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:43,820
You're also an undercover agent?

167
00:13:45,940 --> 00:13:47,820
We still share the same goal.

168
00:13:49,020 --> 00:13:50,300
No wonder I got it wrong.

169
00:13:52,460 --> 00:13:53,740
Then who is

170
00:13:54,460 --> 00:13:55,580
the real Guzhou?

171
00:14:16,260 --> 00:14:19,980
♪The waves♪

172
00:14:20,060 --> 00:14:24,260
♪When will you stop
looking through them?♪

173
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:28,300
♪Missed the time
when the sun was restored♪

174
00:14:28,380 --> 00:14:32,460
♪What else do you expect to like?♪

175
00:14:32,500 --> 00:14:35,220
♪I thought you were an angel♪

176
00:14:35,300 --> 00:14:37,500
♪An angel who watched over me♪

177
00:14:37,540 --> 00:14:40,580
♪And saw every side of me♪

178
00:14:40,660 --> 00:14:43,220
♪Until reality is flooded♪

179
00:14:43,300 --> 00:14:45,460
♪You become sensible♪

180
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:50,020
♪You are finally
out of touch with reality♪

181
00:14:50,340 --> 00:14:52,860
♪I hear the mountains, the seas,
and the people♪

182
00:14:52,940 --> 00:14:54,900
♪All clamoring because of you♪

183
00:14:55,020 --> 00:14:56,980
♪Hiding in the cape after the rain♪

184
00:14:57,140 --> 00:14:59,420
♪I cannot hear you♪

185
00:14:59,460 --> 00:15:02,940
♪So I opened my arms one last time♪

186
00:15:03,100 --> 00:15:06,460
♪But you escaped through the gap♪

187
00:15:06,580 --> 00:15:08,780
♪I saw winters come and summers go♪

188
00:15:08,820 --> 00:15:10,940
♪And thought there was ample time♪

189
00:15:11,180 --> 00:15:12,980
♪Cannot withstand the waves♪

190
00:15:13,100 --> 00:15:15,060
♪But you always make me panic♪

191
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:19,380
♪How ridiculous, making me learn♪

192
00:15:19,460 --> 00:15:22,740
♪How much I am worth♪
